{"tid":2517104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓諧星批評AV女優身材似水果 涉性騷擾恐受查","createTime":"2021-05-05T06:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T06:26:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da7259017db2e97f330215a721ded9d91a8ebcc2","tid":2517104,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iHgA77x-me7ejiu991nTd5zkaPY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VTM7OQEHXZAQTJDZG4ULTZPLFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiHgA77x-me7ejiu991nTd5zkaPY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVTM7OQEHXZAQTJDZG4ULTZPLFE.jpg&h=97df3b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國諧星李昶浩憑扮演「富三代李浩昌」一角而人氣急升，不過近日他因拍攝以日本AV女優為主題的YouTube片而引起韓國網民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n用生果作比喻<br />\n早前李昶浩跟另一諧星宋怜拮合作拍攝YouTube片，二人於片中進行了「AV女優理想型世界盃」。網民指二人的對話幾乎「19禁」而且用詞不當，對AV女優的外貌和身形進行品評。當提到「AV的風格」時，李昶浩表示：「風格非常多。」把多數AV女優特定身體部位比喻成生果等，被批評是涉嫌性騷擾的言論。<br />\n<br />\n引爭議後被刪<br />\n網民又批評於大多數人可瀏覽，而且沒有年齡限制的YouTube，公開這類涉及性的對話，為此表示擔憂，留言「孩子也看了，居然上傳這種東西」、「應該要舉報」等。而《我獨自生活》女星朴娜萊，早前因將男性公仔擺出各種不雅動作，被網民炮轟涉性騷擾，更因而接受警方調查，因此有網民認為李昶浩及宋怜拮亦應該受查。<br />\n<br />\n目前引起爭議的影片已被刪除，李昶浩及宋怜拮未就刪除影片一事發表立場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aMHQh-cQacoBDcn6kJQBJ51FC7s=/802x452/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N4V45YUAABFUBC4G5675LJ2O6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaMHQh-cQacoBDcn6kJQBJ51FC7s%3D%2F802x452%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN4V45YUAABFUBC4G5675LJ2O6I.jpg&h=eec4531f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BMO3HnmRqqnMlloSzLpyls1hW1k=/802x453/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EAWELM4VWVFQPIRJCGHAGEVUF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBMO3HnmRqqnMlloSzLpyls1hW1k%3D%2F802x453%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEAWELM4VWVFQPIRJCGHAGEVUF4.jpg&h=94836685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HmWrEaNfOMLbpW5oTZ1tThhGMJk=/802x454/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XHNYKSUJIVBYFI3YZLKTE4COGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHmWrEaNfOMLbpW5oTZ1tThhGMJk%3D%2F802x454%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXHNYKSUJIVBYFI3YZLKTE4COGE.jpg&h=beb11e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210505/UFJOCFLBWJEVBLH5ZJM7QXSCSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210505%2FUFJOCFLBWJEVBLH5ZJM7QXSCSM%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=76886522\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210505%2FUFJOCFLBWJEVBLH5ZJM7QXSCSM%2F&h=a41f3e9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210505/UFJOCFLBWJEVBLH5ZJM7QXSCSM/</a>"},{"pid":"f132d7258718164107655110c396d56099fa21da","tid":2517104,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"seed?"},{"pid":"a9f9854afd2f0ffb6212266e56be3af5e2726305","tid":2517104,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"又睇av..<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d004e712ddf18755bcbdeb86a36ea108e4477546","tid":2517104,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"抵啦 唔識尊重女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.